---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';

const title = `A Brief Interrogation of ${SITE_TITLE}`
---

<!doctype HTML>
<html>
    <head>
        <BaseHead title={title} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
        <style>
            main {
				width: 960px;
			}
			main h3 span {
				text-shadow: 3px 3px 10px black;
			}
            ul, li {
				margin-top: 0px;
			}
			ul li {
                list-style-type: none;
			}
			ul li p {
                line-height: 30px;
				margin-bottom: 10px;
			}
            .inner-list li {
                margin-top: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 0px;
                list-style-type: disc;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <main>
            <ul>
                <div class="special-box">
                    <h3 class="center-text">🗂️ <i>A Brief Interrogation of Grayvox</i> 🗂️</h3>
                    <br>
                    <li id="question-one">
                        <h4>What's with the name?</h4>
                        <p>
                            I always wanted my username to involve 'Gray' or at least a wolf. After a ton of brainstorming, I came up with this.
                        </p>
                        <br>
                        Other name ideas were:
                        <ul class="inner-list">
                            <li>HowlingGray</li>
                            <li>SystemGray</li>
                            <li>VoxelWolf</li>
                            <li>GraySystems</li>
                            <li>DevByGray</li>
                        </ul>
                        <br>
                        Still hate that last one...
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-two">
                        <h4>Why a wolf?</h4>
                        <p>
                            I could be cheesy and say it's because they're "misunderstood", but I like being original.
                            Put simply, I love wolves. Beautiful, intelligent, a bit scary... and yes, misunderstood.
                            Though I do have a lot in common with them; They're extremely social creatures (unlike me), 
                            do well in packs (unlike me)... wait a minute-
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-three">
                        <h4>What sort of work do you do?</h4>
                        <p>
                            Yes.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            ...A lot of stuff, put simply. Whatever comes to mind, whatever I fancy at the time. 
                            I code stuff, write stories, draw stuff, design games, produce ideas upon ideas upon ideas 
                            upon... well, you get the idea.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <!-- 
                        <li><b>CPU:</b> Intel i7-13700K</li>
                        <li><b>GPU:</b> GeForce RTX 3060 12GB</li>
                        <li><b>RAM:</b> 32GB DDR5</li>
                        <li><b>Hard Drive 1:</b> Samsung 990 EVO 1TB SSD</li>
                        <li><b>Motherboard:</b> MSI Z790-A PRO MAX WIFI</li>
                    -->
                    <li id="question-four">
                        <h4>What are you working on right now?</h4>
                        <p>
                            Whatever my brain decides made sense. I try to keep that up to date on my <a href="/#status">
                            Status</a> though.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-five">
                        <h4>Favorite programming language?</h4>
                        <p>
                            Every language is a tool, each with it's own uses, pros and cons. So I don't have a favorite yet.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            ...But don't worry, if I did, it wouldn't be Java. <i>*shudders*</i>
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-six">
                        <h4>Favorite game?</h4>
                        <p>You think I can name just one? Fool. Here is a list I wrote simply because.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>⛏️ Minecraft</li>
                            <li>👻 Phasmophobia</li>
                            <li>🎥 Content Warning</li>
                            <li>💀 Undertale</li>
                            <li>💜 Heartbound 💛</li>
                            <li>🔍 Tangle Tower</li>
                            <li>👁️ OMORI</li>
                            <li>🐤 Stardew Valley</li>
                            <li>☢️ Lethal Company</li>
                            <li>🏔️ Celeste</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>Of course, that's subject to change over time as I will never stop playing games.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-seven">
                        <h4>Favorite TV show?</h4>
                        <p>...I just said earlier- Fine. Use another singular. But I will stick to my lists.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>❤️‍🩹 Arcane</li>
                            <li>🌲 Gravity Falls</li>
                            <li>🦉 The Owl House</li>
                            <li>🥬 Avatar: The Last Airbender</li>
                            <li>🪦 Lockwood and Co... <i>*sobbing*</i> GIVE IT BACK, NETFLIX-</li>
                            <li>🧙‍♂️ Merlin</li>
                            <li>🕵️‍♂️ Sherlock</li>
                            <li>🐕 Bluey</li>
                            <li>⚔️ She-Ra and the Princesses of Power (Netflix)</li>
                            <li>🦁 Voltron (Netflix)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-eight">
                        <h4>Favorite movie?</h4>
                        <p>...You really don't learn do you...</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>🕷️ Spider Man: Across the Spider-Verse</li>
                            <li>🛰️ Interstellar</li>
                            <li>📜 National Treasure</li>
                            <li>👰 The Princess Bride</li>
                            <li>✉️ Klaus</li>
                            <li>🤖 Wall-E</li>
                            <li>🐹 Bolt</li>
                            <li>🐉 How to Train Your Dragon</li>
                            <li>🫏 Shrek</li>
                            <li>🍳 Tangled*</li>
                        </ul>
                        <span class="mini-text">*I was forced into putting that on here. You know who you are.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-nine">
                        <h4>...Favorite book?</h4>
                        <p>. . . <b>You-</b> Fine. Just take the list.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>🎭 The Phantom of the Opera</li>
                            <li>🤕 Unwind</li>
                            <li>🏹 The Hunger Games</li>
                            <li>🔱 Percy Jackson and the Olympians</li>
                            <li>🏺 Heroes of Olympus</li>
                            <li>👴🏻 The Giver</li>
                            <li>🪦 Lockwood and Co (...yes, again)</li>
                            <li>🌫️ Mistborn</li>
                            <li>💍 The Lord of the Rings</li>
                            <li>⛰️ The Hobbit</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-ten">
                        <h4>Do you enjoy long walks on the beach?</h4>
                        <p>
                            ...Yes? I do? Actually I love the beach, and the mountains, but scenic walks on the beach 
                            are like no other, really. Especially when you're right at the water's edge, and the waves 
                            hit your feet- . . . oh wait, now I know what this is about-
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-eleven">
                        <h4>And how rich are you?</h4>
                        <p>...Oh I see how it is.</p>
                        <p>
                            Well rich enough, thank you. I can live in a cave with what would barely pass as WiFi, 
                            thank you very much.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li id="question-twelve">
                        <h4>Are you actually a wolf?</h4>
                        <p>...This Q&A session is over. <i>*runs*</i></p>
                    </li>
                </div>
            </ul>
        </main>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>

